        "timestamp": "2021-09-10 20:14:08.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4: Code-Review-1\n\nWe are in trouble with a 64 character limit on the config map: Let's use\n\npolicy-clamp-cl-pf-ppnt\npolicy-clamp-cl-http-ppnt\npolicy-clamp-cl-k8s-ppnt",
